OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779106274
OL,3,CFootage shows moment police raid
OL,4,Ccannabis farm above takeaway
OL,6,FA cannabis farmer has been jailed
OL,7,Fafter a large number of plants were
OL,8,Fdiscovered above a takeaway in
OL,9,FMaidstone.
OL,11,FEmiljano Barjamaj was sentenced to one
OL,12,Fyear in prison for producing cannabis
OL,13,Fand abstracting electricity without
OL,14,Fauthority, after he tapped into the
OL,15,Felectrical grid.
OL,17,FDetectives searched an address in
OL,18,FSandling Road on 1 October 2021.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
