FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779106274
OL,3,CFootage shows moment police raid
OL,4,Ccannabis farm above takeaway
OL,6,FOfficers discovered Barjamaj tending
OL,7,Fto a cannabis cultivation and arrested
OL,8,Fhim.
OL,10,FAn engineer later went to the property
OL,11,Fand confirmed the electricity supply
OL,12,Fhad been tampered with so the drugs
OL,13,Fcould be grown.
OL,15,FThe plants and associated equipment
OL,16,Fhave since been destroyed.
OL,18,FBarjamaj, 38, of Kingsley Road, was
OL,19,Fconvicted following a trial and
OL,20,Fsentenced at Maidstone Magistrates'
OL,21,FCourt on Monday 11 May.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
