OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779106274
OL,3,CFootage shows moment police raid
OL,4,Ccannabis farm above takeaway
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Hayley Chilmaid
OL,7,Fsaid: "Barjamaj initially denied
OL,8,Fstealing electricity to cultivate his
OL,9,Fcannabis crop but was proven to be
OL,10,Fboth a thief and a drugs farmer thanks
OL,11,Fto our officers' thorough
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,F"Drugs have a detrimental impact on
OL,15,Fcommunities, with dealers frequently
OL,16,Ftargeting vulnerable users.
OL,18,F"We are pleased to have stopped this
OL,19,Fsupply at source and prevented
OL,20,FBarjamaj further profiting from
OL,21,Fillegal activity."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
